a really loving person,

00:13:16.690 --> 00:13:19.350 align:middle line:84%
then, it will be easy to
have the right relationship

00:13:19.350 --> 00:13:21.100 align:middle line:84%
because other people
will really like you,

00:13:21.100 --> 00:13:23.510 align:middle line:84%
because you'll be loving
and loving towards them.

00:13:23.510 --> 00:13:26.200 align:middle line:84%
If you are a person who
is very self-centered

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:29.440 align:middle line:84%
and you say, well, I want the
right person to make me happy,

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.915 align:middle line:84%
everybody you try to find
will become disgusted with you

00:13:31.915 --> 00:13:33.790 align:middle line:84%
very shortly, because
they don't want to just

00:13:33.790 --> 00:13:35.352 align:middle line:90%
be there making you happy.

00:13:35.352 --> 00:13:37.310 align:middle line:84%
They're looking for
someone to make them happy.

00:13:37.310 --> 00:13:38.200 align:middle line:90%
You follow me?

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:40.090 align:middle line:84%
So in other words, you'll
never get enough of each other

00:13:40.090 --> 00:13:42.790 align:middle line:84%
if you're both in it for what is
the other one going to give me.

00:13:42.790 --> 00:13:43.590 align:middle line:90%
That isn't love.

00:13:43.590 --> 00:13:45.280 align:middle line:90%
That's possessiveness.

00:13:45.280 --> 00:13:47.020 align:middle line:90%
That's attachment.

00:13:47.020 --> 00:13:50.110 align:middle line:84%
So the key point here
is if you understand

00:13:50.110 --> 00:13:52.150 align:middle line:84%
your interconnectedness
with the world,

00:13:52.150 --> 00:13:55.180 align:middle line:84%
and if you understand that
your own state of mind

00:13:55.180 --> 00:13:56.710 align:middle line:84%
is where real
happiness comes from

00:13:56.710 --> 00:13:58.778 align:middle line:84%
or real suffering
comes from, then you

00:13:58.778 --> 00:14:00.320 align:middle line:84%
go to work on your
own state of mind.

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:04.280 align:middle line:84%
If your kids are flunking, you
try to be more kind to them.

00:14:04.280 --> 00:14:05.970 align:middle line:90%
You try to help them study.

00:14:05.970 --> 00:14:08.410 align:middle line:84%
You sort of become content
with whatever it is.

00:14:08.410 --> 00:14:10.930 align:middle line:84%
You affirm that you'd
love them nevertheless,

00:14:10.930 --> 00:14:12.250 align:middle line:90%
no matter what they do.

00:14:12.250 --> 00:14:13.960 align:middle line:84%
You give them a
sense of support.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:16.900 align:middle line:84%
You don't scream and freak out
and intimidate them, et cetera.

00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:20.050 align:middle line:84%
In other words, if you have
the sources of happiness,

00:14:20.050 --> 00:14:23.920 align:middle line:84%
the wellsprings of happiness
in your own inner contentment,

00:14:23.920 --> 00:14:27.010 align:middle line:84%
your own inner
self-sufficiency, so to speak,

00:14:27.010 --> 00:14:29.560 align:middle line:84%
then the world won't
bother you that much.

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:31.420 align:middle line:84%
You can take whatever
