00:14:31.420 --> 00:14:33.850 align:middle line:84%
you'll naturally be
such a cheerful person

00:14:33.850 --> 00:14:36.670 align:middle line:84%
that you'll gravitate
towards more friendly people.

00:14:36.670 --> 00:14:38.890 align:middle line:84%
And you will actually
have better relationships.

00:14:38.890 --> 00:14:41.410 align:middle line:84%
But the key to it is, Corinne,
that the Buddha said, well,

00:14:41.410 --> 00:14:44.410 align:middle line:84%
now I understand, it is
the self-centeredness,

00:14:44.410 --> 00:14:48.760 align:middle line:84%
this self-preoccupation that
makes people discontented

00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:50.020 align:middle line:90%
all the time and dissatisfied.

00:14:50.020 --> 00:14:51.687 align:middle line:84%
