what is that one surefire
way to be miserable?

00:14:57.550 --> 00:15:00.190 align:middle line:90%
Stop to think how happy you are.

00:15:00.190 --> 00:15:02.080 align:middle line:84%
Oh, am I as happy
as I was yesterday?

00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:02.710 align:middle line:90%
Oh, could I be more happy?

00:15:02.710 --> 00:15:04.240 align:middle line:84%
>> I wonder how long
this is going to last.

00:15:04.240 --> 00:15:04.870 align:middle line:90%
>> How long is it?

00:15:04.870 --> 00:15:06.490 align:middle line:84%
Then, immediately, you're
miserable because you

00:15:06.490 --> 00:15:07.698 align:middle line:90%
know it won't last that long.

00:15:07.698 --> 00:15:08.500 align:middle line:90%
It could be better.

00:15:08.500 --> 00:15:10.750 align:middle line:90%
It has been better.

00:15:10.750 --> 00:15:13.250 align:middle line:84%
This relationship is it
great, as good as it could be?

00:15:13.250 --> 00:15:15.040 align:middle line:84%
Oh, no, maybe I should have a
relationship with another one

00:15:15.040 --> 00:15:15.840 align:middle line:90%
and another one.

00:15:15.840 --> 00:15:18.460 align:middle line:84%
Divorce number one,
two, three, four, five,

00:15:18.460 --> 00:15:22.070 align:middle line:84%
it goes on and on like that
