00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:52.270 align:middle line:84%
by developing a way of
getting free, breaking free

00:15:52.270 --> 00:15:54.430 align:middle line:84%
from the inner voices
of discontentment,

00:15:54.430 --> 00:15:56.620 align:middle line:84%
the inner voices of
self-preoccupation,

00:15:56.620 --> 00:15:58.730 align:middle line:84%
by meditation and
by understanding.

00:15:58.730 --> 00:16:00.370 align:middle line:84%
And the more you
break through, you

00:16:00.370 --> 00:16:03.730 align:middle line:84%
can be so contented that you
